// ============================================================
// fieldrun LOGIC EXPORT — LO3a: CONTEXT-FREE WHOLE-MODEL forward pass as ONE Datalog program.
// Input:  token(pos,id) facts (an ARBITRARY context — provide via `-F <dir>/token.facts`).
// Output: decide(v) = argmax next-token id; logit(v,s) = the full scoreboard.
// Weights are FACTS; the forward pass (RMSNorm, RoPE attn, SwiGLU MLP, unembed, argmax) is RULES.
// NOTHING is specialised to a context (unlike export --logic / stitch): swap token.facts and
// Soufflé recomputes from scratch — it answers contexts the exporter never saw. This is LO3a.
// exp(x)=E^x, sqrt(x)=x^0.5, RoPE sin/cos = precomputed per-position facts ⇒ plain Datalog, no FFI.
// config: n_layer=2 H=4 nkv=4 hd=8 d=32 ffn=64 vocab=31 tied=true qk_norm=false
// floats: theta=10000 eps=0.000001   RoPE tables: positions 0..23
// Run: souffle <this>.dl -F <ctxdir> -D -     (ctxdir/token.facts holds `pos<TAB>id` rows)
// ============================================================

